The courses will be held in form of webinars ad are made publicly available. 
The webinars will be differentiated in terms of content, in order to provide a comprehensive training experience, and focused respectively on the following topics:
•	Overview if the multiple benefits;
•	How to assess multiple benefits;
•	Use of the tools produced by the M-BENEFITS project.
The webinars will be designed to last 60-120 minutes including a FAQ-session. Each webinar will be recorded and published on the M-BENEFITS Youtube-channel.
